title: Update parachain-template-runtime.
doc:
- audience: Runtime Dev
  description: |
    Updates the parachain template XCM configuration to better reflect common parachain patterns:
    - Changed native asset from relay chain token to parachain native token (`RelayLocation` â†’ `NativeLocation`)
    - Updated XCM barrier to allow unpaid execution from Asset Hub instead of the relay chain,
      reflecting the shift towards Asset Hub as the primary system parachain for asset operations
    - Added foreign location-to-account mapping using `HashedDescription` for better cross-chain account derivation
    - Enabled local XCM execution by changing `XcmExecuteFilter` from `Nothing` to `Everything`
    - Simplified barrier configuration and added support for known query responses
crates:
  - name: parachain-template-runtime
    bump: minor
